<description>pSearches for all instances of the string codeneedle/code in the given string codehaystack/code and returns the location and range./ppstronghaystack/strong: String to look for codeneedle/code in/ppstrongneedle/strong: String to find in codehaystack/code/ppstrongreturns/strong: Nil if codeneedle/code is not found. An array of arrays with each entry having index zero equal to the position codeneedle/code was found and index one equal to the length of codeneedle/code if codeneedle/code. There is one array entry for each instance of codeneedle/code that is found./p</description>
